iga, a tokom posebnih akcija knjige moete kupiti i sa popustima do 90% na odreene naslove. Za sve kupovine iznad 2000 dinara kao poklon birate jedno od izdanja Knjiare Roman. Za porudbine iz Srbije u iznosu veem od 2000 dinara dostava kurirskom slubom je besplatna. Za kupce iz Beograda dostupna je dostava danas za danas. Porudbine iz inostranstva isporuujemo kuriskom slubom DHL.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.18.0\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_3\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.18.0\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" text_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<p>KONTAKT</p>\n<p>Knjiara Roman</p>\n<p>Gusinjska 7/10, 11050 Beograd</p>\n<p>0114053820</p>\n<p>info@knjizararoman.rs</p>\n<p>PIB: 111911781</p>\n<p>MB: 21568147</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_code _builder_version=\"4.18.0\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d11327.043923794252!2d20.515791!3d44.785678!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x475a70983ee42e1b%3A0x1d86ca1bbbed26c!2sGusinjska%207%2C%20Beograd!5e0!3m2!1sen!2srs!4v1662404316860!5m2!1sen!2srs\" width=\"400\" height=\"250\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>[/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.18.0\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_3\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://dstojanovic.wppsbootcamp.com/roman/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/banca_intesa.png\" _builder_version=\"4.18.0\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" title_text=\"banca_intesa\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_image src=\"https://dstojanovic.wppsbootcamp.com/roman/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/26016-3-major-credit-card-logo-clipart.png\" 